data.description: Short Sale. HERE IT IS!! **LAKE VIEW WATERFRONT** (SHORT SALE) With interest rates in the 6's, it'll go quickly, so don't miss out!!  This charming 3/2 home offers a picturesque lakefront view on just over a half-acre property. With recent upgrades including a new roof, 2 new front windows, 24 x 24" porcelain tiles and an above ground pool with an upgraded pump. The interior boasts a modern touch. The kitchen features solid wood cabinets, granite countertops, and new stainless steel LG refrigerator. Additionally, the home includes an 18 month old LG front load washer and dryer for added convenience. Enjoy a comfortable and stylish lifestyle in this well-maintained residence.  Conveniently located, this home offers easy access to nearby shopping centers and restaurants, providing residents with a variety of options for dining and retail experiences just a short distance away.
